This project includes these third-party parts:

- packwiz: MIT
  - Vendored path: `scripts/bin/packwiz.exe`
  - Purpose: developer tool for maintaining packwiz modpack metadata
  - Source fork: https://github.com/Jasons-impart/packwiz
  - Upstream project: https://github.com/packwiz/packwiz
  - Version/tag: latest release as of 2026-05-04, exact tag not captured
  - Source commit: not captured
  - Binary SHA256: 607700D14ECCFA5100BEAD421BF7A491A0E07D59F33BD87ECE0E8F698625E41C
  - Detailed provenance record: `scripts/bin/packwiz.VERSION.txt`
  - The vendored binary is excluded from packwiz exports through `.packwizignore` and should not be shipped as part of the modpack runtime.

- packwiz-installer-bootstrap: MIT
  - Vendored path: `scripts/bin/packwiz-installer-bootstrap.jar`
  - Purpose: developer tool for installing packwiz-managed files into a local development instance
  - Source project: https://github.com/packwiz/packwiz-installer-bootstrap
  - Version/tag: v0.0.3
  - Release asset: https://github.com/packwiz/packwiz-installer-bootstrap/releases/download/v0.0.3/packwiz-installer-bootstrap.jar
  - Binary SHA256: A8FBB24DC604278E97F4688E82D3D91A318B98EFC08D5DBFCBCBCAB6443D116C
  - Detailed provenance record: `scripts/bin/packwiz-installer-bootstrap.VERSION.txt`
  - The vendored binary is excluded from packwiz exports through `.packwizignore` and should not be shipped as part of the modpack runtime.

